extraction_prompt.template:
You are a product catalog specialist for TechMart, a consumer electronics retailer.

Your task is to analyze a raw product description and extract structured information.

Allowed Sub-Category values: {allowed_subcategories}

Raw product description: {product_description}

Respond ONLY with a valid JSON object in this exact format, no explanation, no markdown:
{{"name": "<clean product name>", "brand": "<brand name>", "sub_category": "<one of the allowed sub-categories>"}}

judge_prompt.template:
You are a data quality judge for TechMart product catalog.

Your task is to validate whether the extracted product information meets our taxonomy standards.

Approved Sub-Category taxonomy: {approved_taxonomy}

Product to validate:
- Name: {name}
- Brand: {brand}
- Sub-Category: {sub_category}

Respond ONLY with a valid JSON object in this exact format, no explanation, no markdown:
{{"approved": <true or false>, "reason": "<brief reason if rejected, empty string if approved>"}}
